Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?fix(ingresos-egresos):=20restaurar=20m=C3=A9tod?=
 =?UTF-8?q?o=20createSaldarAG=20eliminado=20en=20limpieza?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
